Coordinator (English & Business Department)
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/04/30 09:04:00
Ref. JB3045758
Job Description
Position Summary:
This position requires to effectively coordinate the training courses that are delivered in the Training Center. The applicant must have Bachelor Degree/ Diploma in Business Administration (or relevant field) with minimum 2 years of experience in educational institutes in UAE and/or GCC / Middle East. Also, he/she should have good IT and communication skills and should be fluent in both – English and Arabic.
Key Responsibilities:
1.	Handling the Registration Procedures.
2.	 Following up the students list and submitting report to the Training Manager.
3.	Arranging the training manuals, folders, notepads, pens, disks and others for new courses.
4.	Handling the break sessions in coordination with the Administration Supervisor.
5.	Coordinating with the Technical Support Technicians to ensure that the class room has the required equipments.
6.	Handling the attendance on daily basis and making reports accordingly.
7.	Handling the complaints from the candidates and taking actions accordingly.
8.	Additional tasks may be delegated as per the requirement.
Skills
The applicant must have good interpersonal skills, good IT skills and should be fluent in both – English and Arabic
Education
Bachelor Degree
